title: Why Emma Willis won't be having any more children with Matt Willis as she gushes about 10-month-old daughter
text:
Get celebs   Thank you for subscribing!   
Emma Willis has revealed she won't be having any more children with her husband Matt Willis following the birth of their 10-month-old daughter Trixie Grace. 
The Voice host - who is also mum to eight-year-old daughter Isabelle and six-year-old son Ace - recently gave birth to their third child and was adamant she's not having any more. 
Describing her new daughter as "amazing" and the "perfect child," on Loose Women, Emma explained: "She has just slotted in but because I know this is my last. 
"I’m taking every single little bit in because I know I won’t do it again." Read More
